com.gargoylesoftware.htmlunit.html.serializer

Class HtmlSerializerVisibleText

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gargoylesoftware.htmlunit.html.serializer.HtmlSerializerVisibleText

  • public class HtmlSerializerVisibleText
extends Object
    Special serializer to generate the output we need at least for selenium WebElement#getText().

    This is also used from estimations by ComputedCSSStyleDeclaration.

    Author:
    Ronald Brill, cd alexndr
